review_data.title: Great view and good food
review_data.content: Located in a small mountain in Zurich the restaurant has a great view of the region. Food is good and service is really nice. You may find two rooms: one more typical and touristic and another less typical.

review_data.title: Nice Location
review_data.content: Visited here last week. The restaurant is very nice and the staff were very good. The food for me was ok but nothing to rave about. You couldn’t have described it as cheap . Doubt if I will be back.
